Invocation Name: contact andromeda
des:
Play an interactive science fiction-themed story with sound effects and prompts. 
Listen to this story about an Andromedan you name, who reminds you that Earth is really in space too, and the Sun is a star too, right here in the milky way, so why build polluting rockets and destroy a beautiful vacation destination in the milky way? Maybe we should progress in understanding how to preserve this invaluable heritage, and not pollute it with rockets?
Get ready for laughs and giggles as players fill in the blanks. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
